The Kingdom #1
A monster is murdering Supermen throughout time, and now it's up to the Batman, Superman and Wonder Woman of the KINGDOM COME universe to meet their present-day counterparts and save the DCU! Don't miss this follow-up to KINGDOM COME revealing the impact of the next generation of heroes! 

The Kingdom #2
THE KINGDOM concludes as the KINGDOM COME Superman, Batman and Wonder Woman arrive in today's DC Universe to seek the aid of their counterparts to combat the greatest menace ever known. At stake is all of history... and the conclusion to this final battle is something no one expects!
